    "The labels for the weights and biases are w ij and b ij, respectively.",
    "In this example, the i and j values represent rows and columns of the ANN structure, respectively.",
    "In general, a larger ANN has multiple inputs and multiple outputs, with each corresponding to a different feature in the input and output data.",
    "The nodes operate collectively to produce an arbitrary function of the input.",
    "The literature refers to the collection of weights and biases as parameters of the network."
